  ('A WRINKLE IN A TIME','adventure','2018-03-15','2018-04-03',187,'wrinkle.jpg','Young Meg, along with his younger brother and school friend decides to go in search of his father, a physicist, who disappeared in the course of a scientific experiment. To find it is not in the usual world, but in the mysterious fractures of time and space, where the concept of reality is relative and nothing can be believed! Get out of the fantasy worlds and defeat the darkness that spreads through the universe, you can only learn yourself and accept their shortcomings.',1);

